pan class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">fieldset</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">fields</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">metadata</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>The XML entry</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"xml\" data-index=\"4\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">field</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t</span><span class=\"mtk12\">name</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;show_text&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t</span><span class=\"mtk12\">type</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;text&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t</span><span class=\"mtk12\">label</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;COM_FOOS_FIELD_TEXT_SHOW_LABEL&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t</span><span class=\"mtk12\">default</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Hi&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk17\">/&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>turns Joomla into the following HTML code for the output in the backend form:</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"html\" data-index=\"5\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;control-label&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">label</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">id</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;jform_request_show_text-lbl&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">for</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;jform_request_show_text&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    COM_FOOS_FIELD_TEXT_SHOW_LABEL</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">label</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">div</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;controls has-success&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">input</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk12\">type</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;text&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk12\">name</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;jform[request][show_text]&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk12\">id</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;jform_request_show_text&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk12\">value</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Hi&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk12\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;form-control valid form-control-success&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk12\">aria-invalid</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;false&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk17\">/&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">div</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>With <code class=\"language-text\">type=\"text\"</code> we use one of the simplest form fields, that is the one of type <code class=\"language-text\">text</code>. Various types of form fields are built into Joomla. The Joomla documentation lists these standard types. Take a look at the table on the website <a href=\"https://docs.joomla.org/Form_field/en\">docs.joomla.org/Form_field/en</a>. Often you can implement a special requirement with a special field.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"test-your-joomla-component\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#test-your-joomla-component\" aria-label=\"test your joomla component permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Test your Joomla component</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>install your component in Joomla version 4 to test it: Copy the files in the <code class=\"language-text\">components</code> folder to the <code class=\"language-text\">components</code> folder of your Joomla 4 installation. A new installation is not necessary. Continue using the ones from the previous part.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>switch to the Menu Manager and open a created menu item or create a new one. Here you will now see a text field where you can insert any text.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1f3af051301c461beb026999bdf1bef0/191e2/j4x6x1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Request Variable at Joomla Menu Item - Backend\"\n        title=\"Joomla Request Variable at Joomla Menu Item - Backend\"\n        src=\"/static/1f3af051301c461beb026999bdf1bef0/5a190/j4x6x1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1f3af051301c461beb026999bdf1bef0/772e8/j4x6x1.png 200w,\n/static/1f3af051301c461beb026999bdf1bef0/e17e5/j4x6x1.png 400w,\n/static/1f3af051301c461beb026999bdf1bef0/5a190/j4x6x1.png 800w,\n/static/1f3af051301c461beb026999bdf1bef0/c1b63/j4x6x1.png 1200w,\n/static/1f3af051301c461beb026999bdf1bef0/29007/j4x6x1.png 1600w,\n/static/1f3af051301c461beb026999bdf1bef0/191e2/j4x6x1.png 1836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>now switch to the frontend view. Make sure that the text you entered for the menu item is displayed in the correct variant in the frontend.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fd17bc74a942ddcdf58082bff0cb04ea/191e2/j4x6x2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Request Variable at Joomla Menu Item - Frontend\"\n        title=\"Joomla Request Variable at Joomla Menu Item - Frontend\"\n        src=\"/static/fd17bc74a942ddcdf58082bff0cb04ea/5a190/j4x6x2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fd17bc74a942ddcdf58082bff0cb04ea/772e8/j4x6x2.png 200w,\n/static/fd17bc74a942ddcdf58082bff0cb04ea/e17e5/j4x6x2.png 400w,\n/static/fd17bc74a942ddcdf58082bff0cb04ea/5a190/j4x6x2.png 800w,\n/static/fd17bc74a942ddcdf58082bff0cb04ea/c1b63/j4x6x2.png 1200w,\n/static/fd17bc74a942ddcdf58082bff0cb04ea/29007/j4x6x2.png 1600w,\n/static/fd17bc74a942ddcdf58082bff0cb04ea/191e2/j4x6x2.png 1836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I'm sure you can think of funnier or more useful examples. But the sense and function of the variables will be clear.</p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Create multiple menu items, each containing different text. Don't just output the text on the frontend, style the output using <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/if...else\">conditional statements</a>[^developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/web/javascript/reference/statements/if...else]. A popular use case is to change the design of the output using variables. For example, you use the variable to query whether the content is to be output in a list or in a table.</li>\n</ol>\n<img src=\"https://vg08.met.vgwort.de/na/98d3772e579c429fa2b4b823195b57b5\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" alt=\"\">\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    borde